-- MOVES-MainStay Investments hires Brendan Gundersen from BlackRock iShares
-- 
-- Mon Dec 22, 2014 12:45PM EST
-- None



Dec 22 (Reuters) - New York Life Insurance Co's [NYLIN.UL] subsidiary MainStay Investments named Brendan Gundersen as managing director to lead its institutional intermediary channel.

Gundersen will report to Stephen Fisher, co-president of New York life investment management and president of MainStay Investments.